<TEXT>
MOTOROLA'S share price rose sharply yesterday on record fourth-quarter sales
and earnings, driven by strong growth in the US electronics manufacturer's
communications and semiconductor businesses, writes Louise Kehoe.
The share price rose Dollars 10 7/8 to Dollars 123 1/4 , a 52-week high, at
the close in New York.
