FT  15 JAN 93 / World News in Brief: Eruption kills volcano experts
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Four scientists were killed and eight injured in southern Colombia when a
volcano erupted as they worked near its crater. Ten more people are missing.
They were attending a vulcanology conference at a nearby town.
